@startuml A6_sequence_bloody_wolf_demo
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #DC2626
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  ParticipantBorderColor #CBD5E1
  NoteBackgroundColor #FEE2E2
  NoteBorderColor #DC2626
}
title Bloody Wolf Demo — Detection Sequence

actor "Attacker" as ATK #FEE2E2
participant "Endpoint\n(Windows 10)" as EP
participant "SentinelUZ Agent\n(monitoring)" as AGENT
participant "Django REST API" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "IT Manager\nDashboard" as UI

ATK -> EP : Deliver phishing email\nwith STRRAT payload attachment
EP -> EP : User opens attachment
EP -> EP : STRRAT.jar executes\n(Java-based RAT)

AGENT -> EP : Process snapshot (30s cycle)
EP --> AGENT : Running processes:\n  java.exe (parent: outlook.exe)\n  cmd.exe (parent: java.exe)\n  powershell.exe (parent: cmd.exe)

AGENT -> AGENT : Check process hashes
note right: SHA-256 of STRRAT.jar\nmatches MalwareBazaar record

AGENT -> AGENT : Check process chain\noutlook → java → cmd → powershell
note right: Suspicious chain flag triggered\nOffice spawning Java spawning shell

AGENT -> AGENT : Check known tool list
note right: STRRAT in known RAT list

AGENT -> AGENT : Compute delta score:\n  HASH_MATCH: +40\n  SUSPICIOUS_CHAIN: +25\n  KNOWN_ATTACK_TOOL: +30\n  Total: 95 (CRITICAL)

AGENT -> API : POST /api/agent/alert/\n{score: 95, flags: [HASH_MATCH,\nSUSPICIOUS_CHAIN, KNOWN_ATTACK_TOOL],\nprocesses: [...], endpoint_id: 7}

API -> DB : Alert.objects.create(\nseverity=CRITICAL, score=95)
API -> DB : Event.objects.bulk_create(\nall captured processes + network)
API --> AGENT : 200 {alert_id: 142}

UI -> DB : polling GET /api/alerts/
DB --> UI : Alert #142 — CRITICAL — score 95
UI -> UI : Red badge appears\nCRITICAL alert notification

note over UI
  IT Manager sees:
  "CRITICAL alert on DESKTOP-7F3K2
   Score: 95 | STRRAT detected
   Flags: HASH_MATCH, SUSPICIOUS_CHAIN"
end note
@enduml
